== History == DealerTrack purchased Arkona Inc in 2007 for 58.9 million.<ref>{{cite web | url=http://ir.dealertrack.com/releasedetail.cfm?ReleaseID=239820 | accessdate=2009-11-09 | date=2007-04-27 | title=DealerTrack to Acquire Arkona, Inc. | publisher=PR Newswire }}</ref>
== Inventory == Arkona systems export inventory by using an automated report and ftp-exporting program provided by Arkona. They have control over the time the report is run and exported. Arkona sets arbitrary limitations on this ftp script and will not permit DNS hostnames for the FTP host thereby requriing IP address. In addition, usernames and passwords over 10 characters are prohibited.
== Official Documentation ==
You can find much of the official documentation for arkona on [http://www.google.com/search?q=site%3Ahttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.arkona.com%2Fsupport%2F+ext%3Ahtml their website, which is indexed by google], or their [https://www.arkona.com/website_09/support/wiki/login.php|official wiki (login required)].
